Register custom qualifier annotation types to be considered_when autowiring beans. Each element of the provided set may_be either a Class instance or a String representation of the_fully-qualified class name of the custom annotation._

Note that any annotation that is itself annotated with Spring's_{@link org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Qualifier}_does not require explicit registration._@param customQualifierTypes the custom types to register
codeText: public void setCustomQualifierTypes(Set<?> customQualifierTypes) {_		this.customQualifierTypes = customQualifierTypes__	}
